{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_tippi_set_1", "eventName": "獲獎感言", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "獲獎感言", "storyInfo": "昔日輝煌的製片廠面臨倒閉，蒂比不得不與即將離開藍卡塢的同事分別。三人潛入製片廠的倉庫，只為再見一次當年共同寫下的簽名。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g13_directorstudio", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卓越影業，自創立以來辛苦經營十餘年，拍攝了眾多膾炙人口的深夜影片。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最鼎盛的時候，我們的攝影棚沒有一天空閒，影院的午夜場全是我們出品的電影。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這兩年來，我們的票房成績越來越差，幾部大製作電影接連失利。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在就連肥皂劇的導演都可以隨便拒絕我們的邀約，說我們是不入流的製片公司，只會拍一些無聊的血腥片段。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經營不善是事實，資金不濟也是事實。坦白說，我們已經沒有機會拍下一部電影了。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我也不得不承認，沒有人願意看血腥和暴力的片子了。我們被市場拋棄了。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位員工們，我努力過了，你們也努力過了。但在此，我也不得不通知大家……", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卓越電影製片廠……將在一週後正式關閉。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g9_outsidestudio_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，說得那麼煽情，最後還不是一分錢遣散費都不給！想開除人不給錢就直說啊！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然是破產，那肯定沒有錢能給吧……", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就聽他騙你吧。他現在正左手倒右手，準備開下一家電影公司呢。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不信你看看上週的報紙怎麼寫的，都是路人皆知的事情了！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但既然要開新的電影公司，為什麼不把我們招回去繼續做呢？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人家要做超級大片，想賺更多人的錢。而我們是靠血漿和尖叫賺錢的，這種東西怎麼可能放得進他的新電影裡？", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……那我們還找得到工作嗎？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比怎麼也垂頭喪氣的？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你這兩年參與了不少大製片廠的電影吧？你都已經打出名氣了，肯定不會吃不上飯的。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……蒂比？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，我得去找老闆談談。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g13_directorstudio", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，我有事——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，我在最後的會議上已經說得很明白了，我現在已經是個身無分文的窮光蛋了。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然很想給你們補償，但眼下的情況就是——片廠破產了，我一分錢都拿不出來。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，老闆，我不是為這件事來的。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……喔？那你是來和我告別的？", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的好心我收下了，但不用急著告別。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是暫時不開公司了，不代表我之後不做電影。我相信我們很快能在別的片場見面——", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，老闆，我也不是為這件事來的。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你是為什麼來的？", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是來問問……倉庫裡的那些背景板之後會怎麼處理？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……背景板？", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是之前拍電影時製作的背景，應該都存放在辦公室後面的道具倉庫裡——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，我想起來了。前兩天財務還特意跟我說，光是為了存放這些木板，兩年下來讓我多花了一百五十三萬租金。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一百五十三萬金券……把這些背景板送進木材廠都不一定值三萬金券呢。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經叫了人過來處理它們，送進木材廠，還是砍碎當柴燒……算了，愛怎麼樣怎麼樣吧。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可、可是這些是許多人的心血，也是許多觀眾的回憶……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人在乎一個爛片公司製作的背景嗎？", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，我承認你是一位出色的布景噴畫師，你在新片《嗜血午夜》裡的表現讓所有人感到驚豔。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實講，我自己看那些場景的時候，都不敢相信它們其實是一堆塗上顏料的木板。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是為什麼你會從這些資質普通的人裡面脫穎而出。你的能力優於劇組裡的所有人，你畫的東西能得到更多人的喜歡。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但《嗜血午夜》賠了三千萬，是我們虧損得最慘的電影，沒有之一。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "編劇、導演、攝影、演員，沒有一個厲害的，你繪製的背景板再精美又有什麼用？", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觀眾不買帳，電影就沒有票房。公司沒有業績支撐，自然就沒有新的電影，這再正常不過。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人總是要進步的。我拍了十幾年的恐怖片，現在也該去迎合更多的觀眾了。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道不想讓更多人看見你的作品嗎？想的話，就往更高處走。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，別人不知道你的身世，但我知道的。回去問問你的爺爺，他也會認同我的觀點。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果所有人都能多為製片廠著想一點，如果大家能跟上時代潮流，這裡也不會變成現在這幅落魄樣子。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……我可以留下其中一幅背景嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也不行。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "製片廠花錢僱用你繪製這些背景，然後拍成電影，製作成數以萬計的錄影帶流入市場。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼電影畫面裡的所有東西都屬於卓越影業，你畫的背景當然也包括在內。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以翻翻哥倫比亞的版權法，上面也白紙黑字這麼寫著。", "name": "製片廠老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_bar_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比年紀還小，就用果汁代替……來吧，各位，乾完這杯，我們就各奔東西了。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來。", "name": "場記&蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$clink"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$clink", "loop": "false", "channel": "1", "delay": 0.04}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$clink", "loop": "false", "channel": "2", "delay": 0.06}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "loop": "false", "channel": "d1", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "loop": "false", "channel": "d2", "delay": 1.6}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，你也別悶悶不樂了。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些事你不知道，但其實不少人都清楚老闆要關掉這個小工坊，去投資他心裡想的那些“大電影”，只是時間早晚的問題罷了。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你想要的那塊背景板。相信我，你後面畫的每一幅背景，都會比它要好。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你的能力已經被大製片廠認可，他們有充足的資源，你會有更多機會實現自己的想法的。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們從這離開以後，準備再去哪個片廠工作？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認識一些不錯的雇主，說不定能幫到你們……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我嗎？算了算了。找個拍廣告的工作吧，有些廣告公司就喜歡招拍過電影的人。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，當然前提是他們沒看過我拍的電影。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾琳呢？我看你這半年都在看徵人廣告，怎麼樣，找到喜歡的工作了嗎？", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，我有這麼明顯嗎？！", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我用過那個徵人網站，所以有一次看到你在看的時候，一眼就認出來了。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這樣啊……", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實說，我也不知道自己接下來該做什麼……", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來到這個片廠的四年裡，我能做的只有打板、記鏡號，打板、記鏡號。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在叫我去做別的工作，我也拿不定主意……也許回老家重新學一門別的手藝，安分過日子會更適合我吧。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大家都要離開藍卡塢嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小蒂比，我能力沒你強，運氣也沒你好。我就是入行比你早點，見過的噁心事比你多點。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，還能靠摸著一台攝影機吃飯，已經很好了。是不是藍卡塢，沒有那麼重要。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於大部分人來說，卓越影業的工作，也只是一份工作而已。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時候你堅持一份工作很久，最後發現它並不適合你，這很正常。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在藍卡塢，想成名的人太多，能成名的人太少。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是和你們一起拍電影的時光，對我來說很幸福！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我看來，你們並不比那些拍商業大片的人差，反而在很多時候比那些大片廠的人更有人情味。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是為什麼，我依然想在這裡和你們共事。我真的很想和你們再多拍幾部電影……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個老闆根本沒有理由拋棄你們……！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有你的這句話，就足夠啦。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我一開始來藍卡塢，是因為在學校表演裡被人誇演技好。但來到這裡以後，發現自己就是一個平凡無奇的普通人。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是蒂比，以你的才能，我相信你最後一定會成為寫進藍卡塢影史的噴畫師的。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你天生就是吃這碗飯的人，所以你一定要在藍卡塢堅持下去。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有一天你能站在領獎台上領獎，我說不定也會因為跟你共事過，跟老家的人到處吹牛呢！", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……可是……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，本來說好了一起喝酒罵老闆的，怎麼搞得這麼難受！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在酒吧裡沒有人了，不然我們一起再放個電影看吧。喝喝酒，看看電影，聊聊天，就跟以前一樣。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次……讓蒂比來挑一部電影？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想想，那就看……我們第一次合作的電影，《壞小子》吧。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，我多少還是有點電影品味的，真不想看自己拍的爛片啊！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬修，既然都是最後一次了，就按照蒂比說的來吧。", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好吧。那就看《壞小子》。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_bar_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老舊到偏色的投影機發出嗡嗡的散熱聲，三個人圍在小小的圓桌前，看著最後緩緩滾動的演職員表。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……噗。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈……", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*藍卡塢片場術語*，這也太尷尬了！這個男的為什麼最後能殺到領獎台啊！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時拍的時候怎麼沒人罵編劇在想什麼啊？", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不知道……可能就是導演想再要一場血腥戲吧……哎喲，我笑得肚子好痛！", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這個鏡頭……你當時……當時為什麼要把人鼻孔拍得那麼大啊？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我也不知道啊！我拍了那麼多條，怎麼能想到最後剪進去一條最醜的啊！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不行了……哈哈哈，徹徹底底的爛片！", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哈……對！這個片的背景也粗糙得要命，全部都是我熬了幾天幾夜趕出來的。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我每次看到最後，都想衝上去把我的名字從演職員表裡摳掉……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你竟然還看了很多遍？我從來都不看的！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小蒂比難道會自己偷偷在家欣賞參與過的電影？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才、才沒有！我只是單純很喜歡這個電影的最後一幕……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個最莫名其妙的一幕？哈哈哈哈哈哈……", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是。我喜歡這幕的背景，那個粗糙的領獎台。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們也許不記得了……這塊背景板的後面，有整個劇組所有人的簽名。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等……有嗎？", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的。拍這部電影的時候，我剛剛加入，製片廠也因為經濟困難，說是快要倒閉……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本請的演員怕我們發不出薪水，臨時拒絕了拍攝計劃。之後投資方又突然撤資……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道……那個時候我們都以為這就是最後一部電影了，想著能拍完就是勝利。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當時好像還去臨演裡拉了一個最上鏡的，臨時做我們的男主角……", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個簽名，就是最後殺青的時候，大家一起簽的。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的我們拍完了，不是嗎？而且票房竟然意外地不錯，甚至有影院第一次為我們排了白天的場次！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些為了迎合觀眾刻意加的血腥場面，是我們所有人不得已為之的選擇，但觀眾卻覺得很精彩很爽快。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然苟延殘喘了兩年，製片廠最後還是倒閉了……但我想說，我們已經拯救過它一次，我們並不是失敗者！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比……所以，你還想挽留我們？", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，我知道你想鼓勵我們。但這一次，製片廠再也沒有復活的可能了……", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我尊重你們的選擇。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我只想在大家離開之前，再看看那個背景板後的簽名……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們想去嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "微弱的燈光照亮一件件蒙塵的道具，自化作影像刻錄進膠片裡後，它們便一直封存於此。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳咳咳咳……到處都是灰，嗆死人了！", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）馬修，小點聲！門口還有警衛呢，萬一被發現怎麼辦！", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（摀住嘴巴）唔……嗯。", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）這些背景板堆起來比好幾個我加起來還高……沒想到我們居然一起拍過這麼多電影！", "name": "場記"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）哼，你別說這麼厚的背景板了，你記錄的表格、我拍過的膠片，哪個堆起來沒人高？", "name": "攝影師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"timr": 3.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我找到了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g10_stage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三人移動到一幅背景板前，即使過了兩年，上面的顏料依舊和當初一樣鮮豔。"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們把它翻過來。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pullcurtain", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“最後的電影”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "導演   本·羅伊", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主演   索菲婭·瑪奇   瑞安·哈里斯", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "攝影   馬修·托馬斯", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "噴畫師   蒂比·布克", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "場記   艾琳·亨特", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們看……這就是我們的“光輝事蹟”。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“最後的電影”，但並非最後一部，我們拯救過這裡。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡堆積如山的背景板，全是我們一起工作的見證。我們一起拍過的場景，甚至可以鋪滿整個星光大道！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（啜泣）", "name": "馬修"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬修……你還好嗎？", "name": "艾琳"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒事……我、我就是……有點喝多了！", "name": "馬修"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強壯的男人此刻正努力地讓自己的啜泣聲變小。而艾琳的眼眶也明顯濕潤了。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比牽起身旁兩人的手，緩緩朝背景板前走去。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按《壞小子》裡的劇情，現在我們已經逃出了監獄，殺光了會場裡所有的反派，然後站上了領獎台——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，作為藍卡塢最好的攝影師，馬修·托馬斯先生！還有藍卡塢最佳場記，艾琳·亨特女士！你們有什麼想說的嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想說……", "name": "馬修"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（大聲）卓越影業，*藍卡塢片場術語*！", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "馬修&蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（更大聲）藍卡塢，*藍卡塢片場術語*！*藍卡塢更專業的術語*！", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……卓越影業，*藍卡塢片場術語*！", "name": "馬修"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藍卡塢，*藍卡塢片場術語*！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三人的聲音在倉庫裡久久地迴盪，直到回聲完全消失，三人才發出止不住的笑聲。"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈……我喝多了……今天我們都喝多了……！", "name": "馬修"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛我的腦子裡，突然閃過了拍電影的這幾年，跟夢一樣……太快了！", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊……跟夢一樣。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比緊緊地握住馬修和艾琳的手，並將它們緩緩舉起。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，現在，該我們向所有觀眾謝幕了。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉起手臂）", "name": "馬修"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉起手臂）", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，要是現在有一束聚光燈就好了……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$tactfulboost", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比的話音未落，突然一束強烈而奪目的光線照在了三人身上，晃得他們睜不開眼。"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰在那裡？不准動！", "name": "保全"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把手舉起來！", "name": "保全"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好……剛才喊太大聲被發現了！我們要跑嗎？", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……必須跑！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等下！", "name": "馬修"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼了？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們就要過來了！", "name": "艾琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然都被發現了，不如……我們一起把這個領獎台偷走？", "name": "馬修"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比深吸了一口氣，她能感受到光束搖晃得越來越劇烈，也離他們越來越近。"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡這個主意。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那晚，藍卡塢的街頭突然出現了一幅巨大的移動背景板，背景板上畫著一座巨大的領獎台。"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使在光怪陸離的藍卡塢，這樣匪夷所思的場景也並不多見。於是，人人紛紛舉起相機記錄。"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們拍到領獎台在藍卡塢星光大道的人行道上，在名人館的大門前，在電影廣場的正中央……"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但不知為何，沒有人清楚拍到扛著背景板的人，大家只能隱約看到三個模糊的身影。"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這三個人的身分並沒有引起太多人的關注，這件趣事也只是被作為談資在飯桌上一笑而過。"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟對於藍卡塢來說，能成名的人太少，想成名的人太多。這件事倒是再正常不過。"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}